  "description": {
    "en": "Comprehensive open-source databases containing historical tennis rankings, match results, and statistics for both men's (ATP) and women's (WTA) professional tennis. Includes match-level data from 1968 to present, player biographical information, and detailed match statistics. The datasets cover tour-level, challenger, futures, and qualifying matches with extensive historical coverage.",
    "zh": "全面的开源数据库，包含男子（ATP）和女子（WTA）职业网球的历史排名、比赛结果和统计数据。包括从1968年至今的比赛级别数据、球员传记信息和详细的比赛统计。数据集涵盖巡回赛级别、挑战赛、未来赛和资格赛，具有广泛的历史覆盖范围。"
  },
